The Philippines deaths by age group for 2020 from the World Population Prospects 2019

deaths_wpp_2019.Rd

The Philippines deaths by age group for 2020 from the World Population Prospects 2019

deaths_wpp_2019

Format

A tibble with 4 columns and 21 rows:

area

Area i.e., country

year

Year i.e., 2015-2020

age_category

Five-year age groups

death

Number of deaths

Source

World Population Prospects 2019
